  "texts": [
    "Moreover, there is a risk of bias and discrimination if the AI system is trained on data that is not representative of the diverse population of children with autism [9].",
    "Therefore, it is essential to carefully consider the ethical implications of using AI in education for children with autism.",
    "In conclusion, utilizing AI in education can transform how we think about learning and support children with autism to achieve their full potential.",
    "Research Methodology InformantsThe study used purposive sampling to select 20 informants who met specific criteria.",
    "These individuals were parents or educators of autistic children and had valuable experience using AI-powered interventions to improve their children's learning and social communication skills."
  ]
}